      * Variables received from the input string
     D WSUSER          S             10
     D WSTUR           S              8
     D BSTUR           S              8  0
N01  D WSUNIK          S              9
N01  D BSUNIK          S              9  0
     D DOCLNK          S            200
N03  D DOCTYP          S             35
     D DOCTXT          S             35
     D Error           S            150
     D JSONstring      s          64000
     D ANTLEST         s              9  0
      * For xlate mellom Upper Case og Lower Case
     D UC              C                   CONST('ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRST-
     D                                     UVWXYZÆØÅ')
     D LC              C                   CONST('abcdefghijklmnopqrst-
     D                                     uvwxyzæøå')
      *get input-string
